Please see the API documentation of Net_UserAgent_Mobile_Display class. - Added support for DoCoMo's P252iS, D506i, F506i. - Added support for EZweb's W21H, A5504T, TK41. ** NOTE ** In the next release, BC will be broken for PHP5 compatibility reasons. Please see bug #827.
